IBAN,com,operates,as,a,web,based,solution,that,supports,the,validation,and,calculation,of,International,Bank,Account,Numbers,IBAN,This,platform,uses,algorithmic,formulas,to,determine,the,validity,of,IBANs,The,IBAN,Recovery,API,provides,a,mechanism,for,randomly,retrieving,characters,from,an,IBAN,This,functionality,allows,users,to,randomly,identify,illegible,parts,of,an,IBAN,The,RESTful,API,sends,HTTP,formatted,requests,and,returns,XSD,formatted,responses